Treasury balances at the FederalReserve rose on April 6 to 4.262 billion dlrs from 3.876billion dlrs on the previous business day, the Treasury said inits latest budget statement.    Balances in tax and loan note accounts fell to 4.950billion dlrs from 5.004 billion dlrs on the same respectivedays.    The Treasury's operating cash balance totaled 9.212 billiondlrs on April 6 compared with 8.880 billion dlrs on April 3. Reuter&#3;